- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses the complexity of cut-elimination and introduces a new method to control it. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper discusses the complexity of cut-elimination and its implications for computation.
